NNAAMMEE
       ii..ccllaassss   -  An imagery function that generates spectral signatures for
       an image by allowing the user to  outline  regions  of  interest.   The
       resulting signature file can be used as input for _i_._m_a_x_l_i_k or as a seed
       signature file for _i_._c_l_u_s_t_e_r.
