TTHHEE MMEENNUUSS
       All of the menus in the _i_._c_l_a_s_s program are displayed across the bottom
       of the graphics monitor in the Menu Frame.  To select  an  option  from
       one  of  these  menus,  simply place the cursor over your selection and
       press any button on the mouse.  Each of the menus is discussed  in  the
       following paragraphs.

   TThhee CCoommmmaanndd MMeennuu
