       _Z_o_o_m   This  command allows the user to outline a rectangular region in
              either the Map or Zoom Display Frames and  the  region  is  dis-
              played,  magnified,  to  fit  in  the Zoom Display Frame.  A red
              rectangle is drawn in the Map  Display  Frame,  indicating  what
              area the Zoom Display Frame shows.


       To outline the rectangular region simply use any mouse button to anchor
       the first corner of the border and then use any button  to  choose  the
       other corner.

       _D_e_f_i_n_e _r_e_g_i_o_n
