              play Menu allows the user to redraw map display frames.

       _A_n_a_l_y_z_e _r_e_g_i_o_n
              This selection starts the process  of  analyzing  the  currently
              defined  region.  A histogram of the defined region will be dis-
              played for each band.  On the histogram for each band, the mean,
              standard  deviation,  minimum  cell value and maximum cell value
              are marked.  The  histograms  are  automatically  scaled  in  an
              attempt to fit the data into the space available, but it is pos-
              sible that all of the data will not fit.  In this case, as  much
              of  the data as possible, centered around the mean, will be dis-
              played.  After the histograms are displayed, the  user  will  be
